<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUS I COME</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka gikpuok, lungkham leh thim apat,
 Isu, ka hung! Isu ka hung!
 Suohchakna, nawpna leh vakna mun,
 Isu, ka hun zuon ie!
 Ka damlohna Na hihdamna ah,
 Ka taksapna, Na neihzawhna ah;
 Ka gitlohna apatin nang kawm,
 Isu, ka hun zuon ie!

[V2]
 2. Ka zahchak, titloh leh manna' pat,
 Isu ka hung! Isu ka hung!
 Na Kross zieka lawkna lopi chuh,
 Isu ka hun zuon ie!
 Lei lungkham apat na hihdamna,
 Damsung tuilien Na suk hai dingin;
 Lungkham apat nawpna la sa di'n,
 Isu, ka hun zuon ie!

[V3]
 3. Kisaktheih leh buoina apatin,
 Isu, ka hung! Isu ka hung!
 Nang deihdan thilbawl nuom zing dingin,
 Isu, ka hun zuon ie!
 Ka mihinna pat Nanga cheng di'n,
 Dahna 'apat chunglam nawpna mu di'n;
 Chunglama vakhu banga lengin,
 Isu, ka hun zuon ie!

[V4]
 4. Lauhum leh than kihchakna apat,
 Isu, ka hung! Isu ka hung;
 Na In nawpna leh vakna mun chuh,
 Isu, ka hun zuon ie!
 Gentheih guollouh sietna mun apat,
 Na venbitna huong sung nuom lamah;
 Na mel lopi chuh mu zing dingin,
 Isu ka hun zuon ie!</lyrics>
<hymn_number>163</hymn_number>
</song>